<i>adjective</i>: 요염하다 [요염하다] <i>determiner</i>: 매혹적 [매혹쩍], 고혹적 [고혹쩍] <i>noun</i>: 매혹적 [매혹쩍], 뇌쇄 [뇌쇄/눼쇄] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요염하다 [요염하다]</dt><br>
<dd>bewitching; fascinating; sexy</dd><br>
<dd>상대방의 정신을 흐리게 할 만큼 매우 아름답다.</dd><br>
<dd>Beautiful enough to make someone feel stunned.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매혹적 [매혹쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>captivating; fascinating</dd><br>
<dd>남의 마음을 완전히 사로잡는 힘이 있는.</dd><br>
<dd>Having the power to captivate someone's mind completely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고혹적 [고혹쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>alluring; fascinating</dd><br>
<dd>정신을 차리지 못할 만큼 아름답고 매력적인.</dd><br>
<dd>Being so beautiful and attractive that a beholder cannot come to his/her senses.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매혹적 [매혹쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>captivating; fascinating</dd><br>
<dd>남의 마음을 완전히 사로잡는 힘이 있는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Having the power to captivate someone's mind completely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뇌쇄 [뇌쇄/눼쇄]</dt><br>
<dd>fascinating; enchanting</dd><br>
<dd>이성을 매혹하여 심하게 애가 타게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>Stealing the heart of someone, by seducing him/her.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>